==Description==
The '''Ochre Shard''' is a type of [[Underground|Underground Item]] first encountered in [[Hoenn]].

==Details==
The Ochre Shard can be used, alongside [[Quest Points]] {{Questpoints}}, to purchase items at the [[Shard Trader|Shard Traders]].

==Mine Layout==
The Ochre Shard appears in the Underground as a 4x3 sized object.<br><br>
[[File:OchreShardMine.png|100px]]

==Trades==
Ochre Shards can be used together with other [[Shards]] to purchase the following items:
